John Cosgrove (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Cosgrove_(actor) 0 John Cosgrove (1867 – 11 August 1925) was an Australian actor, writer and director who worked in theatre and films during the silent era. He sometimes collaborated with Bland Holt. John_Cosgrove ( 1867 – 11_August_1925 ) was an_Australian_actor_,_writer_and_director who worked in theatre_and_films during the_silent_era . He sometimes collaborated with Bland_Holt .
